title: Sju Bonor
description: Eco store Seven Beans is opened by the same people operating Vegeriet restaurant. Sells organic, fairtrade and local produce, and no animal except eggs and dairy products. Freshly baked bread, cakes, crispbread from Vegeriet, muesli, nötblandningar, chocolate, a wide selection of groceries, fresh fruit and vegetables according to availability and season, hair and skin care products, scented candles, textiles in bath and kitchen and also a little children's clothing.
